cast.original_title: Vivre sa vie: film en douze tableaux
cast.overview: Twelve episodic tales in the life of a Parisian woman and her slow descent into prostitution.
cast.title: Vivre Sa Vie

details.biography: Gisèle Braunberger was born on 2 August 1935 in Paris, France. She is an actress and production manager, known for Madame de la Carlière ou Sur l'inconséquence du jugement public de nos actions particulières (1988), En attendant l'auto... (1970) and Astragal (1968). She was previously married to.
details.name: Gisèle Braunberger
